===================
Setup a GeCCSMatrix                                                      [TOC]
===================

In this example we show how you:

- How to setup a general sparse matrix in *coordinate storage*.  This is a
  common step in FEM when the stiffness matrix gets assembled.
- Show how to convert the sparse matrix from the coordinate storage format to
  the *compressed column storage* format.


